# Code Review Checklist

## Automatic Rejection

- ANY hard-coded UUIDs, API keys, credentials, tokens
- ANY `fontSize: spacing.*` usage (use `typography.fontSize.*`)
- ANY `as any` type assertions
- ANY hard-coded hex colors (except in theme files)
- Variables prefixed with `_` that are actually used

## Security & Data

- [ ] No hard-coded UUIDs, org/tenant IDs, API keys
- [ ] All IDs come from Config, AuthContext, or route params
- [ ] No `as any` or `as unknown as <Type>` assertions

## Design System

- [ ] All `fontSize:` uses `typography.fontSize.*`
- [ ] All colors use `theme.colors.*` or `colors.palette.*`
- [ ] All margins/padding use `spacing.*` values
- [ ] Semantic color correctness (angry=errors, success=success states)

## Hook Patterns

- [ ] All API calls use TanStack Query hooks
- [ ] Query keys include ALL parameters affecting result
- [ ] No unnecessary try-catch (TanStack Query handles errors)
- [ ] Conditional queries use `skipToken` or conditional rendering

## Variable Naming

- [ ] `_` prefix variables must be unused - remove underscore if used

## Common Mistakes

- `fontSize: spacing.md` → `fontSize: typography.fontSize.md`
- `locationUuid: 'hard-coded'` → `locationUuid: locationId`
- Unnecessary `try/catch` around API calls
